                                            revenue cycle solutions
                                            

revenue cycle solutions

Huron's revenue cycle solutions are unrivaled in the industry for sustainable revenue cycle improvement, helping clients realize and maintain exceptional revenue cycle performance by drawing on more than 20 years of experience. Huron serves clients across the country, which include large integrated delivery systems, academic medical centers, community hospitals, physicians groups and specialty providers. Huron's depth of expertise and diversity of experience allows us to create a flexible and sustainable strategy that can be deployed broadly across your revenue cycle or with a targeted approach to address your most pressing business needs. Huron works side-by-side with you to embed leading practices into your revenue cycle to realize lasting improvements. In addition to delivering significant, sustainable net revenue gains, Huron's revenue cycle solutions improve operating efficiency, reduce expenses and increase patient, physician and staff engagement and loyalty.
As a trusted strategic advisor, Huron can help you address revenue cycle challenges through the following solutions:

 End-to-end revenue cycle transformation 
 Patient engagement and liability collections 
 Denials management and prevention 
 Revenue cycle operations standardization, consolidation, or centralization
 Hospital and physician revenue cycle integration 
 Health  information system (HIS) conversion support (pre/during/post) 
 HIS optimization to support improved revenue cycle performance 
 Implementation of revenue cycle workflow, reporting and analytics tools
 Evaluation of outsourcing arrangements and/or vendor performance 
 Scheduling and patient access improvements 

To learn more about our capabilities, visit our Revenue Cycle Solutions page.



