                            Patient and caregiver engagement 
                            


                                            healthcare coaching partnerships
                                            

healthcare coaching partnerships
We partner with organizations to achieve better transparency and higher accountability, enabling them to execute effectively. Working side-by-side, we help to establish, accelerate, and hardwire the necessary changes that create a culture of excellence, and improve employee engagement and patient experiences. We have worked to scale our Evidence Based Leadership℠ approach to be effective in large healthcare systems, academic medical centers, stand-alone community healthcare organizations, physician organizations and rural hospitals. We also have tailored our offerings for the emergency department and the Canadian market. 



                                            leader evaluation manager®
                                            

leader evaluation manager®
Studer Group's Leader Evaluation Manager® software is a web‐based application that automates the goal-setting and performance-review process for all leaders, while ensuring that performance metrics of individual leaders are aligned with the organization's overall goals. The Leader Evaluation Manager® software helps leaders understand the key items they are accountable to achieve and which of those are most priority.



