Enterprise Solutions & Analytics - Huron






























 

 










Enterprise Solutions & Analytics
Is it possible to succeed in market conditions undergoing rapid change?
Success hinges on the relationships companies have with their customers and their ability to make insightful business decisions that deliver value. But in constantly evolving industries, these decisions are harder to make, and changes more difficult to manage. The accuracy of a company’s underlying, enterprise-wide systems that support these decisions, as well as compliance and risk protection data, become essential for their future success. As is a deep understanding of a company’s nuanced set of stakeholders, existing governance and processes, and customer relationships.
With seemingly endless options and questions to consider, how can companies choose the right technology and path forward?
At Huron, we understand the complexities of the competitive landscape and statutory regulations facing our clients. That is why we work in partnership with global executives to address the challenging realities they face. Whether that is through Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP), Enterprise Performance Management (EPM), Customer Relationship Management (CRM) or business analytics, we optimize financial performance, achieve operational efficiency, and improve the customer experience. 
As a leader of cloud implementations, we have significant Oracle and Salesforce expertise and are the largest and fastest-growing EPM firm in North America. But we don’t stop there. We continue to challenge ourselves and our clients to adapt and evolve. Because as change is always in motion, so are we.






Advisory Services
Analytics and Reporting
Customer Relationship Management (CRM)
Enterprise Performance Management
Enterprise Resource Planning
Managed Services
Infrastructure and Integration





Our Services


                            advisory services
                            


                                            Overview
                                            

Overview
Whether Fortune 500 or mid-size, emerging or maturing, our team has witnessed what finance and IT organizations do well and where they can improve compared to their peers and competitors. 
Our approach utilizes our unique industry benchmarks and maturity models, along with completely understanding your unique business challenges to help:

Assess existing business processes and evaluate where technology can best be utilized to optimize and streamline these processes
Evaluate the change management impact of process re-engineering, including preparation of technology implementation
Develop a detailed enterprise technology roadmaps including current state, future state analysis
Understand requirements and translate them into the proper design documents to produce an accurate scope (RFP or RFI) for a project

In addition, our roadmaps include:

Maturity model progress plans
Technical hardware blueprints
Phased technology implementation plans
Change management and adoption plans
Risk factors and mitigation plans




                                            Assessments
                                            

Assessments
Huron provides existing enterprise technology customers with the opportunity for an independent third party to review and assess their current solutions.
This comprehensive 2-day session consists of discussions guided by a pre-defined checklist of key inspection points associated with best practices for each application. The discussion focuses on collecting feedback from your unique organization and stakeholders that helps with identifying the root cause of any issues within your applications. Our team will then meet with you to discuss the overall health status of your applications, findings that identify specific issues impacting the health of an application and recommendations categorized into a roadmap of short term and longer term enhancements.



                                            Solution Adoption
                                            

Solution Adoption
A new technology solution can add measurable value to your organization. To ensure adoption and ultimate success, there are a few thing to keep in mind before you begin, including stakeholder engagement, organizational readiness and training. Huron partners with our clients to assess their current state and provide tangible recommendations for moving forward to ensure successful solution adoption. Learn more. 





                            analytics & reporting
                            


                                            Overview
                                            

Overview
We help organizations continuously measure, plan, and act through the use of reporting and analysis tools. Huron provides a cutting edge information strategy approach that can allow your organization to realize the value of your financial and operational technology investments. Let us help you further leverage your investments by integrating your on-premise data, with the ever-increasing amount of cloud, social media and unstructured content, to maximize both customer satisfaction and profitability.
We understand the reporting requirements of your organization today, and can provide solutions that span:

Accounting and financial insights
Departmental analysis and a view into the effectiveness of an organization's operations
Variance reporting across the enterprise
Identifying issues or opportunities and taking action with big data, business intelligence and advanced predictive analytics






